{"type": "article", "id": 51695, "title": "手推车用于收纳成了潮流，这款美观兼具实用性｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-01T23:00:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48891, "name": "Schonbuch"}, {"id": 48892, "name": "Tecta"}, {"id": 45618, "name": "Bisazza"}, {"id": 48893, "name": "Sé"}, {"id": 34472, "name": "BuzziSpace"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 48894, "name": "Wolfgang Hartauer"}, {"id": 48895, "name": "India Mahdavi"}, {"id": 48896, "name": "Ini Archibong"}, {"id": 48897, "name": "Soley Thrainsdottir"}, {"id": 29485, "name": "Alain Gilles"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180401221423MKwgTY3qhX5HNcmP.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Grace bar cart by Sebastian Herkner for Schonbuch</h3><p>德国家居设计师 Sebastian Herkner 为德国品牌 Schonbuch 设计了一款手推车。它有一个优雅的名字 Grace，灵感源自 1950 年代的复古家具。设计师重新构想了在家中品尝鸡尾酒的场景，试图创造一个属于未来的经典作品。</p><p>他使用粉末涂层金属、木材和玻璃创造了一个线条清晰，造型时尚又兼具实用性的手推车。你可以把它看成是一个移动酒吧桌，或是边桌，当然更有创造力的使用办法，是把它用作办公室或是卧室的收纳空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804012215108ZoK1C0xStfFuyk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221510Rj6Xa1DyxOs2o93N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.300000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221510Pv391huQOAlaL8nK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Schonbuch<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kasa stacking bowls by Wolfgang Hartauer for Tecta</h3><p>这个可堆叠托盘 Kasa 出自设计师 Wolfgang Hartauer 之手，他为德国设计品牌 Tecta 创造了这个如同桌面装饰雕塑般的产品。设计师选择了将橡木、枫木和胡桃木三种材质混搭在一起，在 Tecta 精巧的雕琢技术之下，确保三个托盘可以无缝堆叠在一起，亦可单独使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221758D1lWg5Ua6RF0YxTj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.726141\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221758QozRDdj38kAsr96H.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643382\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221758eO12AlfkLv96US5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672397\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221721e7Y0WnGorVCty4kK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672397\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Candy-hued Bathroom Range by India Mahdavi for Bisazza</h3><p>意大利顶级玻璃马赛克制造商 Bisazza，将在今年的米兰家具展上推出新品。法国设计师 India Mahdavi 为其设计了最新糖果色浴室系列，包括浴缸、洗脸水槽和镜子，另有糖果色调的条纹马赛克砖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221827Y5JfIUOD0XEsgdqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.bisazza.it/en-us/news/milan-design-week-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bisazza</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Collection IV by Ini Archibong for Sé</h3><p>去年米兰设计周期间，欧洲家具品牌 Sé 在 Rossana Orlandi 画廊中布置出一间四房公寓发布新系列。这次他们与瑞士产品设计师 Ini Archibong 合作推出的新系列，意在展现深化和灵性，这也是后者最钟爱的主题。</p><p>Ini Archibong 表示，Sé 在豪华家具领域占有一席之地，他的目标是强化 Sé 的美丽，进一步探索高贵、创新的材料，然后用最简单的轮廓和装饰元素将其表现出来，这次用的是玻璃、大理石和黄铜。这把没有椅腿的椅子是其中一件代表作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221859dSeRZmPKEhbM0lfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221859WspnI8SRAvXcrLjo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cleaning Strategies project by Soley Thrainsdottir</h3><p>冰岛艺术大学毕业生 Soley Thrainsdottir 将松针和马脂等材料，设计成了一系列清洁工具和产品，在冰岛的 2018 DesignMarch 设计节期间提出，旨在探索把当地原材料作为可持续清洁工具的潜力。</p><p>她专注于冰岛林业和屠宰行业的肥料，制造刷子、肥皂、清洁喷雾剂和抛光剂。她研究了世界各地不同的清洁习惯，以及人类使用清洁产品的历史。松油的消毒性能使其适用于清洁喷雾剂，同时由于其无划痕和防腐性能，松树灰变成了用于抛光金属和玻璃的黏合剂。</p><p>同时，由于其耐久性和耐热性，马毛被重新用作刷子，马脂被制成肥皂。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221919HayuqjPpeZhtkV4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221920LpoOsEHn2gJFjZuc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221920wveJKTmgC3UlGHFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221920ZvX6ozqkw0PN5gus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221920RQTVrNoHSw3kpl97.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221921EMVfkvyH53NBQmPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/31/soley-thrainsdottir-cleaning-strategies-sustainable-tools-natural-resources-waste-products-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>BuzziHat: A Hat-Shaped Acoustic Lighting Collection by Alain Gilles for BuzziSpace</h3><p>比利时设计师创意家具品牌 BuzziSpace，声称是为明天的美好居家及办公室生活而设计，强调建立在功能性和便捷性之上的创意。这次的新品 BuzziHat 系列，出自比利时设计师 Alain Gilles，不仅能够提供照明功能，还能作为吸音装置。</p><p>BuzziHat 系列的外观就像是可折叠的帽子，帽檐向四周延展开来，俏皮的样式很符合 BuzziSpace 的品牌调性，提供 4 种不同尺寸，以适应不同的空间和声学需求。用户还可以选择各种颜色和面料组合进行定制。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957bpiwAr4Xg5uNE3ev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804012219579lFjwEnSoPkgx5TH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957b1mBUKqJotwD7jYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957ExfXpWBgr38Tkhol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957F31moltZTibX0dYJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957PevDOmzqMbxY5f3J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.314844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180401221957bSUPpCMrZFtiKuAG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/buzzihat-a-hat-shaped-acoustic-lighting-collection-by-alain-gilles-for-buzzispace/buzzispace_buzzihat_gif_animat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}